01:26:45.720 --> 01:26:48.314
I married the girl I love.

01:26:48.440 --> 01:26:51.000
I married her twice.

01:26:51.680 --> 01:26:54.433
And I sang and I played my guts out!

01:26:59.640 --> 01:27:01.995
I shine like gold.

