01:33:27.520 --> 01:33:30.193
And he could not resist her charms.

01:33:30.880 --> 01:33:33.997
Along the way he married and divorced.

01:33:35.120 --> 01:33:37.873
Married and divorced again!

01:33:38.000 --> 01:33:43.028
